1
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:40,960
Put me down

2
00:00:41,119 --> 00:00:42,479
I'm fine

3
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:44,560
Let them come get me

4
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:45,799
Don't worry, Auntie Chen

5
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:47,399
I'll get you there

6
00:00:47,399 --> 00:00:48,359
It'll be fine

7
00:00:48,359 --> 00:00:49,759
Bringing your mom to the hospital again?

8
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:50,560
She's not my mom

9
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,439
She's my neighbor

10
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:52,240
Get her up here

11
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:54,320
Easy now

12
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:56,799
Quick, doctor

13
00:00:58,159 --> 00:00:59,439
High blood pressure caused a coma

14
00:00:59,759 --> 00:01:00,719
Organize emergency treatment immediately

15
00:01:00,719 --> 00:01:01,439
Quick

16
00:01:13,799 --> 00:01:14,599
Auntie

17
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:16,439
You're awake

18
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:18,640
Doctor

19
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:19,400
Doctor

20
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,400
The patient is awake

21
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,040
How do you feel?

22
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,040
Condition is stable

23
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,400
She's out of danger

24
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,760
Just needs to rest

25
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,359
Alright

26
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,159
Thank you

27
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,359
Auntie

28
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,599
You're really lucky

29
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:41,319
If it weren't for this neighbor...

30
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:43,120
...bringing you to the hospital in time...

31
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,840
...you've cheated death twice.

32
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,920
What?

33
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,200
Twice?

34
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:49,760
That's right

35
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,599
Last time you had carbon monoxide poisoning...

36
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,680
...it was this neighbor who brought you here too.

37
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,879
I thought she was your daughter

38
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,480
Your hand

39
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,639
It's nothing

40
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,879
Just some scratches

41
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,800
The nurses insisted on bandaging it

42
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:18,800
Zhen Zhen

43
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,000
How is she?

44
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,199
She...

45
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,840
...has a fracture.

46
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,439
But the doctor said...

47
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,719
...she'll recover soon with treatment.

48
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:36,599
I'm sorry, Zhen Zhen

49
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,479
Move out

50
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,199
Move out?

51
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,719
The Wang family must move out immediately

52
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,520
We're not moving

53
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,400
Or we'll smash everything

54
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,439
What did you say?

55
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,199
Why do we have to move?

56
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:46,759
This house is ours

57
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,439
Who are you?

58
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:50,719
What right do you have to tell us to move?

59
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:51,840
Look clearly

60
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,280
It's in black and white

61
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,599
Your family's house...

62
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,719
...has been mortgaged to us.

63
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:57,240
You took fifty thousand yuan from us

64
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:58,520
Fifty thousand?

65
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:00,479
If you can't pay the principal and interest...

66
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,800
...this house belongs to us.

67
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:11,080
How could Xu Fugui have signed this?

68
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,360
Impossible

69
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,599
He's locked up right now

70
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:17,199
How could this be his signature?

71
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,199
The money...

72
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:20,159
...did your Wang Yingtang take it?

73
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:24,800
Since you admitted to the money...

74
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,000
...the agreement is valid.

75
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:27,800
Either move out...

76
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:30,199
...or pay back the principal and interest.

77
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:33,599
Monthly interest is ten percent

78
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,879
You're loan sharks!

79
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,879
Did you really take fifty thousand from them?

80
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,479
Yes

81
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,080
Mom

82
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:51,520
Little Sister

83
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:53,560
Were you tricked by him?

84
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,319
Opening a vinegar workshop isn't that easy

85
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:57,039
Isn't it easy for Second Sister?

86
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,400
As long as I have the vinegar cellar and secret vinegar recipe...

87
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,240
...I can do it too.

88
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,199
You took the secret vinegar recipe

89
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,719
that your second sister entrusted to me.

90
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,000
So what if I did?

91
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,720
I know a Hong Kong businessman.

92
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,560
I can use the Hong Kong businessman as a partner

93
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,040
to secure the Private business license.

94
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:21,279
That way, my vinegar workshop

95
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,800
will definitely be bigger than Second Sister's.

96
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,240
And I'll definitely make more money than her.

97
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,600
I can give you the best life.

98
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,839
Xiaomei.

99
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:30,319
You were the one who reported the vinegar workshop.

100
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:33,120
You forged your dad's signature

101
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:34,519
and took money from others.

102
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:36,240
Yeah.

103
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:38,120
So what if I sold the house?

104
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,519
I can invest the house money into the vinegar workshop.

105
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:42,040
That way I can make a lot of money

106
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:44,839
and get our family a bigger, better house.

107
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,240
Mom.

108
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,519
You hit me?

109
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:54,240
Didn't you say you loved me the most?

110
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,240
You are so thoughtless.

111
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,639
You ruined your dad.

112
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,199
Our home is gone.

113
00:04:59,199 --> 00:04:59,639
Xiaomei.

114
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,720
You still don't realize you're wrong.

115
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,399
You want our whole family to sleep on the streets?

116
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,560
Mom.

117
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,519
You don't love me the most anymore.

118
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,360
This home is just a house.

119
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,759
What's wrong with letting me use it?

120
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,480
Mom.

121
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,639
Your dad was right.

122
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,720
I spoiled you too much.

123
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:24,160
Something was bound to happen sooner or later.

124
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,199
I've committed a sin.

125
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:32,360
How did I raise such an ingrate?

126
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,279
Stop.

127
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,240
Stop for a moment, everyone.

128
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,639
What are you doing?

129
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:44,800
What are you doing?

130
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,240
What are you trying to do?

131
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,959
I'm only going to say this once.

132
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,399
Starting today,

133
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,199
your Baliang Vinegar Workshop

134
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,800
is mine now.

135
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:57,079
What did you just say?

136
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,000
Say that again.

137
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:12,839
I have a signed agreement.

138
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:14,000
So,

139
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:15,319
the vinegar workshop here

140
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:17,560
and the vinegar cellar are all mine now.

141
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:21,439
Impossible.

142
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:24,040
My dad would never give the workshop to you.

143
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,800
Uncle Xu isn't even around.

144
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,079
How could he possibly sign for you?

145
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,240
It must be fake.

146
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,879
Whether it's true or fake,

147
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,839
let Wang Yingtang tell you.

148
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,639
Wang Yingtang!

149
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:35,480
Wang Yingtang!

150
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:38,480
Wang Yingtang is the one who facilitated this.

151
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:39,639
So,

152
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:43,079
the vinegar workshop and vinegar cellar here

153
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:44,920
are all mine now.

154
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,199
On that agreement of yours,

155
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,800
is it my dad's signature?

156
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,240
Giving away all the shares, right?

157
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,959
Yes.

158
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,439
He holds 100% of the shares.

159
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:53,759
He has already signed,

160
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,480
transferring all shares to me.

161
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,600
So,

162
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:59,480
this vinegar workshop is mine.

163
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,199
Fine.

164
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:02,480
You just wait.

165
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,199
Pretty fierce, aren't you?

166
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,439
What are you doing?

167
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,720
Look clearly.

168
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,720
This is the real share division agreement.

169
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:21,199
The shareholder on this isn't my dad.

170
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:24,199
It's me, Second Aunt, and the Zheng brothers.

171
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:33,079
This... impossible.

172
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,000
What is going on?

173
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,279
You...

174
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:44,160
Wang Yingtang, that idiot.

175
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:46,000
Can't distinguish equity from legal representative.

176
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,160
Let's go.

177
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,519
Jianshe.

178
00:07:57,360 --> 00:08:00,240
The Wang family's daughter saved me twice.

179
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:03,040
I used to tell myself,

180
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:06,120
I'd never forgive the Wang family in this life.

181
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,439
Jianshe.

182
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,720
Aren't you on the day shift?

183
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,800
Where are you going?

184
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,759
I swapped shifts with Xu Fugui.

185
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,519
Isn't tomorrow your birthday?

186
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,000
I want to spend it with you.

187
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,000
I asked him to swap shifts.

188
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,800
Okay.

189
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,680
Then go ahead.

190
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,879
We'll celebrate together tomorrow.

191
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,160
Be careful on the way.

192
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,160
Stay safe.

193
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,160
Every one of your birthdays,

194
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,439
haven't we celebrated together?

195
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,759
Jianshe.

196
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:34,360
I had to find someone to blame.

197
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,000
My heart hurts.

198
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,759
I couldn't get over it.

199
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,120
I couldn't accept it.

200
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:44,159
That you had the accident because you swapped shifts for me.

201
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:49,720
I... I blamed the Wang family over and over again.

202
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:52,519
Pushing all the responsibility onto the Wang family.

203
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,360
Only in this way,

204
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:59,399
could I fall asleep every night.

205
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:02,080
Jianshe.

206
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:05,360
I know Minjiang likes Yingrong.

207
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:08,639
Yingrong is a good girl.

208
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:13,159
But out of a mother's selfishness,

209
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:17,919
I felt Minjiang should be with Zhen Zhen.

210
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:20,720
We should be responsible for Zhen Zhen.

211
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:35,799
Zheng Minjiang.

212
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:36,720
What are you doing?

213
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:41,799
You can't give up on love.

214
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,799
Whoever lives in your heart, is the one.

215
00:09:44,159 --> 00:09:45,360
You can't lie to yourself.

216
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:51,000
You heard everything.

217
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,600
I asked you before,

218
00:09:55,159 --> 00:09:57,159
what a man needs to prepare to confess to a woman.

219
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:58,879
You said,

220
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:00,960
prepare one hundred love letters.

221
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:03,799
But right now,

222
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:06,799
I only have a diary written for you.

223
00:10:07,279 --> 00:10:08,919
I don't know if it counts.

224
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,360
But I can't wait anymore.

225
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:15,600
Wang Yingrong.

226
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:18,159
I... I like you.

227
00:10:22,399 --> 00:10:24,000
Then when I confessed to you before,

228
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,600
you said there was nothing between us.

229
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,159
I was wrong about last time.

230
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:30,159
I used to think

231
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,159
I shouldn't let anyone

232
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,519
have the chance to drag your name through the mud.

233
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,000
That's why I didn't admit it.

234
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:35,840
Now,

235
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:36,960
I regret it.

236
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,000
Actually,

237
00:10:49,879 --> 00:10:51,600
I was the one who fell for you first.

238
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,919
Many, many years ago,

239
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,519
I liked you long ago.

240
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,720
You fool.

241
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,440
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

242
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:11,960
Did... did you...

243
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,360
waver because of what my mom said?

244
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,519
I didn't.

245
00:11:16,759 --> 00:11:18,159
Our feelings for each other

246
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:20,399
and the responsibility to Zhen Zhen are two different things.

247
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:24,879
But...

248
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:27,360
given our current situation,

249
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,720
we can't just pretend

250
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:30,039
that nothing happened

251
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:31,000
and be together.

252
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,720
Now that we know how the other feels,

253
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:37,000
I won't back down.

254
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,559
And I won't give you up to anyone.

255
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,000
But with so much happening right now,

256
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,600
it's not a good time for us to be together.

257
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,320
Let me see what this is.

258
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:51,919
Didn't you say no?

259
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,279
Even if I say no, I still want to see the diary.

260
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:53,679
Alright, alright.

261
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:53,960
Hurry up.

262
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:54,960
Let me see.

263
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,600
If we aren't together,

264
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,960
why should I show you?

265
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:57,960
What are you looking at?

266
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,720
Let me see. Not showing you.

267
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,240
Today,

268
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,679
fetching water at the public kitchen...

269
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:11,480
Stop reading.

270
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,080
Stop reading. Let's go home.

271
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,399
Did you set a trap to cheat me?

272
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,200
Did you?

273
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,600
You told me to mortgage the house

274
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,279
to get a loan for you.

275
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:19,399
I never saw the money; it went right into your pocket.

276
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:20,919
You made me sign a contract in English.

277
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:23,039
You were clearly trying to scam me, right?

278
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:25,320
Who told you not to study hard?

279
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:27,320
Suffering a bit for your ignorance

280
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,559
is perfectly normal.

281
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,159
You really are a merchant's son.

282
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:32,799
The moment money is involved,

283
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:35,120
I don't recognize you anymore.

284
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,399
Yingtang.

285
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,759
Romance and cooperation are different.

286
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,399
Business is business.

287
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:43,600
I must use ruthless tactics.

288
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:45,600
I won't let my dad look down on me again.

289
00:12:46,759 --> 00:12:49,159
Anyway, this agreement doesn't count.

290
00:12:49,519 --> 00:12:50,399
You didn't tell me

291
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:51,600
why the interest was so high,

292
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,600
nor did you clarify how many shares I'd hold.

293
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,799
You just made me use my dad's signature

294
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,159
to confusedly transfer the vinegar workshop's management rights

295
00:12:56,159 --> 00:12:56,960
over to you guys.

296
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,440
And now,

297
00:12:58,639 --> 00:13:00,000
the workshop's management rights and the house

298
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,120
are all yours.

299
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,919
This was clearly a trap set for me.

300
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,960
It's fraud.

301
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:08,840
Yingtang.

302
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,960
It's in black and white.

303
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:12,720
You can't deny it.

304
00:13:14,159 --> 00:13:16,000
Besides, you didn't check clearly first.

305
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,200
Your dad is just the vinegar factory's legal representative.

306
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,799
He has no shares.

307
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:22,480
Your house will be used to cover my losses.

308
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,559
You're despicable.
